{"tid":1495914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想拎百零萬去柬埔寨投資, 求指教","createTime":"2019-08-22T09:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T18:57:31.000Z","uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4347d3ed0d692f95cde0cd8155edef55d8954990","tid":1495914,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"之前唱左D 人仔, 點知而家跌到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加上香港局勢咁唔明朗, 個仆街政府擺明同市民對著幹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連香港班「大媽耍」都調錢走, 所以更加想分散下投資, 目標喺柬埔寨金邊, 做過Fact Check, 呢個地方政局穩定, 冇外匯管制, 用美金交易, 最重要係自己親身去過, 所以對呢個地方有信心, 想睇下其他CHING有咩睇法, 歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說幾個月前, 仲未有6.12事件之前, 我去左柬埔寨首都金邊搵個巴打玩, 因為佢去左果邊做野幾年, 而家好少見到佢, 成日都同我講果邊環境唔差, 叫我過去睇下, 咁岩前排腦細要我清假, 我就拎左幾日AL去搵佢玩下, 講真, 我去之前對呢個地方0認識, 仲問佢果邊會唔會打仗 (因為聽過赤柬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 會唔會好危險, 洗唔洗打免疫針, 當然去完番黎覺得自己好LOW B啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去左4日3夜, 分享下果幾日做過D乜<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">DAY 1</span></span></strong><br />\n落左機之後, 佢接左我去酒店CHECK  IN, 間酒店叫LUMIERE HOTEL, 大約70美金一晚, 唔算平, 唔算貴, 不過質素幾好, 外型都靚仔既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後就去左一間叫香港茶餐廳既地方食LUNCH, 呢個亦都係我第一個驚奇既地方, 原來果邊D消費咁L貴, 我叫左個牛腩面加杯凍檸茶, 竟然要7蚊美金, 冇唸過呢度D消費竟然同香港差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺入面食野既人基本上8成都係外國人, 個FD話因為而家好多外資公司過黎金邊做生意, 加上呢個區係金邊最核心既地段, 所以主要以外籍人士為主<br />\n<br />\n食完野之後佢就帶左去佢住既APARTMENT坐下打FIFA, 2房1廳, 800呎左右, 有露台, 不過外型有D舊, 而且冇咩管理, 但竟然要1200蚊美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話而家既新樓有管理, 開放式都租要1000蚊美金以上, 如果一手買入價大約16萬美金, 嘩, 計番咪成8厘回報? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係唔係真係有咁多人租先? 所以我出於好奇心, 就叫佢帶我去睇下附近D環境啦, 之後就去左睇下同區既樓盤, 基本上出租率都有8-9成, 有2個仲誇張到100%出租, 叫我等半年先黎問, 而且租金絕對唔平, 我個FD話佢當初過黎搵地方住都搵左成個月有多先搵到, 一係太貴, 一係租q哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完野之後就去左食野先, 飲下咖啡, 行下街,  DUP 下骨 (唔好問我正定邪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 夜晚唱下歌, 咁就過左一日, 全程比我最大感覺係貴, 貴, 同貴, 消費真係同香港差唔多, 飲杯咖啡都話要4.8美金, DUP骨同唱歌就唔使講啦, 呢個地方既消費水平真係好高, 完全估佢唔能到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">DAY2</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">休息下先, 下回再講</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd44867f465de169fabb150364f948e88e6788e","tid":1495914,"uid":288742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"柬埔寨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好玩啦"},{"pid":"32abdc3c1445f98c9d2e7f1b8d82119367e961aa","tid":1495914,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dd44867f465de169fabb150364f948e88e6788e","tid":1495914,"uid":288742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"柬埔寨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好玩啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"師兄去過未先"},{"pid":"dd9f92929e05eb217238ea2e35821c0d80ec8d96","tid":1495914,"uid":144248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"巴打 我都喺柬埔寨<br />\n跟老豆嚟闖下<br />\n身邊全部On9大陸佬好撚難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719a93f1146b6b50ce8b44dce33edcecc045fbc9","tid":1495914,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T18:57:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}